DOMAIN SKETCH WITH MANY EXTRA DETAILS :

Note, this is provided as a glossary for the use cases. The use cases should use terminlogy mentioned here.
It extracts a lot of information from the feature list.

Information such as locatino name etc. WILL NOT GO INTO THE DOMAIN MODEL.

This is for use case reference. The domain model is a strict subset of the information provided here.


USER
------
Has a :
	User account

USER ACCOUNT
-------------
Has a : 
	Account Information
	Availability Status
	Contact List
	Visibility List


ACCOUNT INFORMATION
--------------------
Has a :
	username
	password
	email 

	workplace
	name
	gender
	Avatar


CONTACT
-------
Is a :
	User

CONTACT GROUP
--------------
Has :
	Contacts


CONTACT LIST
------------
Has :
	Contacts


VISIBILITY LIST
---------------
Is a :
	Contact List



NOTIFICATION
------------
Has a:
	Poster
	Receiver List
	

POSTER
-------
Is a:
	User

RECIEVER LIST
--------------
Is a :
	Contact List



MEAL NOTIFICATION
------------------
Is a :
	Notification
Has :
	Meal notification Information



MEAL NOTIFICATION INFOMATION
-----------------------------
Has :
	Location
	Duration
	Start time
	End time
	max capacity
	current capacity
	Custom message
	Additional Information


CAPACITY UPDATE NOTIFCATION
----------------------------
Is a :
	Meal Notification 


FRIENDS ATTENDING NOTIFICATION
-------------------------------
Is a :
	Meal Notification
Has :
	Contact List


ACCEPTANCE NOTIFICATION
-----------------------
Is a :
	Meal Notification


CANCELLATION NOTIFICATION
-------------------------
Is a :
	Meal Notification





